ATTRIBUTION NOTICE

This project was architecturally inspired by pluralsh/plural
(https://github.com/pluralsh/plural), an enterprise Kubernetes management
platform by Plural Labs, Inc., licensed under AGPL-3.0 with MIT exceptions.

FluxStream is a fully original implementation written from scratch, adapted
to the OTT/video streaming domain. No source code from pluralsh/plural has
been copied, reproduced, or incorporated into this project. The architectural
concepts (umbrella app structure, RBAC, multi-tenancy, webhook systems,
background job pipelines, GraphQL API patterns) have been re-implemented
independently in the context of a streaming media platform.

This attribution is provided voluntarily in the spirit of open-source
community respect and transparency.
